semble method that we here\ncombine with quantum Monte Carlo -- in studies of quantum phase transitions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 Feb 2001 21:29:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 5 Mar 2002 17:39:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
